      "description": "<p fr-original-style=\"\" id=\"isPasted\" style=\"margin: 0px; width: 100%; line-height: 1.5; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Every 18 months, GEN has the opportunity to participate to earn Casino funds as part of a funding pool kindly assigned for non-profit organizations. &nbsp;This is one of the many ways that the government supports the many non-profit organizations in Alberta. &nbsp;We are assigned two days to staff with volunteers who will handle a number of roles. &nbsp;There is a fixed allocation for meals for volunteers while they are serving on their shift.</p><p fr-original-style=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; width: 100%; line-height: 1.5; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br fr-original-style=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"></p><p fr-original-style=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; width: 100%; line-height: 1.5; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">While use of the funds has specific requirements on how they are spent, this is an important part of GEN&rsquo;s overall budget.</p><p fr-original-style=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; width: 100%; line-height: 1.5; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">What a cool thing to come see and learn about!</p><p fr-original-style=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; width: 100%; line-height: 1.5; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Sign up, and email to <strong fr-original-style=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 700; box-sizing: inherit;\">President@GEN.org </strong>to note shift timeframes that work for you, and any role preferences. &nbsp;We will do our best to accommodate as long as all areas are covered.</p><p fr-original-style=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; width: 100%; line-height: 1.5; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The lead coordinator will assign the roles which include: &nbsp;General Manager, Banker, Cashier, Chip Runner, Countroom Supervisor, Countroom Staff, and Backups. &nbsp;Volunteering is open to both Members and Non-Members of GEN. &nbsp;Members will be gi... 